Class CourseDBElement

java.lang.Object
CourseDBElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<CourseDBElement>
public class CourseDBElement extends Object implements Comparable<CourseDBElement>
This class respresents a course data base elements with a ID, CRN, number of credits, room number, and insturctor name. This class implements the Comparable interface for sorting elements by CRN
Author:
Lima Waziri
